text: Cristian Alexandru Novacek (born 8 February 1996) is a Romanian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Foresta Suceava.Rapid a câştigat amicalul cu Concordia Chiajna. Daniel Pancu a făcut un anunţ trist pentru suporteri la finalul partidei. liga2.prosport.ro ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liga I players Category:CS Concordia Chiajna players Category:Liga II players Category:CS Afumați players Category:ACS Foresta Suceava players
